# llms.txt/llms-full.txt (cmd/conduit/internal/llmsgen) are regenerated by
# `make generate` and diffed byte-for-byte by CI (validate-generated-files).
# Force LF endings so a CRLF checkout (e.g. Windows contributors with
# core.autocrlf=true) can never produce a spurious diff against the
# generator's LF-only output.
llms*.txt text eol=lf
